title: Early hot seat rumblings, Le'Veon Bell trade rumors with Jason La Canfora (Football 10/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to break down the latest NFL news and notes and to look at the latest on the Le'Veon Bell saga and whether or not the running back will be traded. Then Will and Jason break down the coaches who are on the hot seat the most right now and see who could be canned first, all brought to you by ZipRecruiter.
